frames.caption: A muscular figure stands on a ledge overlooking an ancient city, facing a colossal creature emerging from the clouds. The scene is filled with tension as the city below is bustling with people preparing for an impending confrontation.
frames.description: The scene is set in an ancient, labyrinthine city with intricate architecture. A powerful character stands prominently in the foreground, gazing at a massive, intimidating creature that looms over the city. The atmosphere is charged with anticipation and impending conflict.

frames.caption: A muscular figure stands on a ledge overlooking an ancient city, facing a colossal giant emerging from clouds. The scene is filled with tension as the giant appears to be approaching the city, while smaller figures gather below.
frames.description: The scene depicts a dramatic confrontation in an ancient city setting. A powerful character stands ready on a ledge, facing a massive giant that looms over the cityscape, suggesting an impending battle.
